OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA fine
OL,6,Fevening with long sunny spells for
OL,7,Fmany. Cloud reforming overnight,
OL,8,Fespecially across northern and eastern
OL,9,Fcoasts, and spreading inland
OL,10,Fovernight. Remaining largely dry with
OL,11,Fa light northeasterly breeze.
OL,12,
OL,13,CWednesday:FPatchy cloud at first, but
OL,14,Fburning away through the morning.
OL,15,FOtherwise sunny, and turning very warm
OL,16,Fby the afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
