OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FCloudy at times, mainly mornings and
OL,7,Fovernight, with sunny spells each
OL,8,Fafternoon. Breezy, especially along
OL,9,Fthe coast. Very warm on Thursday,
OL,10,Fturning less warm by the weekend.
